parts.text: This document, affirming the public availability of "Client Details - AEC" on a transparency website without exemption, directly reinforces core conservative principles. It exemplifies a commitment to limited government and actively counters potential governmental overreach by ensuring public access to information. Such transparency regarding "Client Details" promotes market freedom and economic efficiency by enabling rigorous public scrutiny of how taxpayer funds are managed, fostering judicious spending, and preventing waste. Ultimately, this transparency serves the national interest by enhancing accountability and underscoring the crucial ideal of a government subservient to the public, rejecting secrecy.
